data.description: Discover your dream home in the desirable Melodie Park neighborhood of South Daytona! This delightful 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom residence offers a unique blend of comfort and convenience. Boasting two primary bedrooms and dual living spaces, the home caters to both relaxation and entertainment. The heart of this home is the beautifully updated kitchen, featuring a sleek 2019 stainless steel range and refrigerator, modern 2020 cabinets, and a stylish butcher block top island. Flexibility is key with a converted 4th bedroom that can easily revert to a garage, alongside a bonus area perfect for a home office. Step outside to embrace the Florida sunshine in your own above-ground pool, surrounded by a private, fenced-in yard. Ideal for family outings, a picturesque park is just a short stroll away.  This property is not just a house, it's a lifestyle waiting for you. Act now to make this inviting pool home your personal paradise!
